data.description: Welcome 8 Woodland Ave!  Open the gorgeous solid wood front door and step into this unique home!  Slate floors lead you thru the foyer to an open concept living space with a view of the stone fireplace from the living room, dining room and den.  Kitchen comes complete with granite countertops, a huge window that spans one side of the room and a breakfast nook.  From the kitchen or dining room, relax in the sunroom with a soak in the hot tub.  Master Bedroom Suite with a full bath and a walk-in closet.  2 add'l bedrooms and a full bath round out the main floor.  Wind down the spiral staircase to the finished lower level where you will find an office, family room, laundry room, work room, and a huge bonus room.  2 sliding glass doors lead to a stone patio surrounded by mature trees and perennials, then stroll down the path to another patio with a stone fireplace.  2 car attached garage completes this home!  Located just off Route 819 on a cul-de-sac minutes from downtown Greensburg.
